# CameraSystem

## Purpose
Updates the orthographic camera each frame in response to keyboard, scroll, and window-resize input
events. Window-resize events update m_AspectRatio and rebuild the projection matrix for ALL cameras
regardless of m_ReactsToInput. Translation (WASD) and zoom (scroll wheel) are applied only to cameras
where m_ReactsToInput = true. Camera matrix is rebuilt every frame an event is present; skipped
entirely when no relevant events arrived.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| KeyPressedEventComponent | read |
| MouseScrolledEventComponent | read |
| WindowResizeEventComponent | read |
| OrthographicCameraComponent | write |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| OrthographicCameraComponent | write | Updates m_CameraPosition, m_ZoomLevel, m_AspectRatio, and the internal view-projection matrix |
